        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:4:133:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/132/5613",
        "text": [
          " اِمْرَأَةٍ مَاتَتْ وَ تَرَكَتْ زَوْجَهَا قَالَ \"فَالْمَالُ كُلُّهُ لَهُ\" قُلْتُ اَلرَّجُلُ يَمُوتُ وَ يَتْرُكُ اِمْرَأَتَهُ قَالَ \"اَلْمَالُ لَهَا\"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.5613 - Muhammad ibn Abi Umayr narrated from Aban ibn Uthman from Abu Basir who reported from Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) regarding a woman who passed away and left behind her husband.\nImam (as) said: \"All the wealth belongs to him.\"\nI asked: \"What if a man dies and leaves behind his wife?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"The wealth belongs to her.\""
          ]
        }
      }
